Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:53.05,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心唱吧 兰歌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.30,0:19:56.72,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替我保护她
